SUMMARY: Springboard March Break Student Job Fair
DESCRIPTION:This event is open to Grade 12 graduates\, post-secondary stu
 dents\, and youth seeking employment opportunities in areas such as camps
 \, recreation\, food service\, and more.\n\nHow to attend:\n1. Register f
 or and attend a free Job Fair Preparation Workshop\n2. Attend the worksho
 p – staff will schedule your virtual intake appointment\n3. Complete your
  virtual intake between March 16–19\n4. After completing your intake and 
 registration\, you may be selected to attend the Virtual Job Fair and int
 erview with employers\n\nJob Fair Preparation Workshops:\n\nMarch 16 – Re
 sume Workshop | 11:00 AM\nhttps://us06web.zoom.us/meeting/register/UkWO-I
 63RwClePFsD06j9A https://us06web.zoom.us/meeting/register/UkWO-I63RwClePF
 sD06j9A\n\nMarch 17 – Interview Workshop | 10:00 AM\nhttps://us06web.zoom
