 tps://us06web.zoom.us/meeting/register/sdyOJQcfR9WG8S_C1P3GTQ\n\nMarch 19
  – Resume Workshop | 10:00 AM\nhttps://us06web.zoom.us/meeting/register/k
 J1mZhKWTf2LLQHWya_18g https://us06web.zoom.us/meeting/register/kJ1mZhKWTf
 2LLQHWya_18g\n\nRegistration and information:\n\nParticipants can registe
 r here:\nhttps://www.eventbrite.com/e/1984885614304?aff=oddtdtcreator htt
 ps://www.eventbrite.com/e/1984885614304?aff=oddtdtcreator\n\nEmployers in
 terested in participating can register here:\nhttps://form.jotform.com/Sp
 ringboardServices/springboard-march-job-fair-march-20 https://form.jotfor
 m.com/SpringboardServices/springboard-march-job-fair-march-20\n\nEmployer
  registrations will be reviewed and our team will confirm participation f
 or the event.\n\nThe event flyer is attached for reference.
