DESCRIPTION:The Spring Art Show and Sale showcases over 400 juried\, orig
 inal works of art created by The Art Guild of Scarborough artists\, many 
 of whom will be in attendance. The art is a variety of mediums including 
 watercolour\, pastel\, oil\, acrylic\, ink\, sculpture and mixed media. F
 ree parking\, admission and refreshments. We look forward to seeing you. 
 More info at theartguildofscarborough.com/upcoming-shows https://theartgu
