SUMMARY: PLANNING AND HOUSING COMMITTEE
DESCRIPTION:Attend the Meeting: Members of the public can attend Planning
  and Housing Committee meetings in person at Toronto City Hall or watch l
 ive via the City of Toronto's YouTube Channel at youtube.com/TorontoCityC
 ouncilLive http://youtube.com/TorontoCityCouncilLive\n\nMake a Deputation
  (Speak at the Meeting): To speak at a meeting\, register in advance by e
 mailing phc@toronto.ca mailto:phc@toronto.ca or calling (416) 392-7033. I
 nclude your name\, contact information\, and the agenda item number and t
 itle you wish to address. Registration deadline: 4:30 p.m. the business d
 ay before the meeting.\n\nSubmit Written Comments: Email phc@toronto.ca m
 ailto:phc@toronto.ca . Indicate the item number and subject in your email
 .\n\nView Agendas & Minutes: toronto.ca/council http://toronto.ca/council
 \n\nGeneral Inquiries: 311 | (416) 392-2489 | 311@toronto.ca mailto:311@t
 oronto.ca\n\nAccessibility Accommodations: accessibility@toronto.ca mailt
 o:accessibility@toronto.ca | (416) 392-5431\n\nStay informed on Ward 23 n
 ews — subscribe to Councillor Myers' newsletter at jamaalmyers.com http:/
 /jamaalmyers.com\n\n
