SUMMARY: Understanding Your Teenager's Personality
DESCRIPTION:Understand Your Teen through their Personality Style – In-per
 son\n\nParenting a teenager can feel confusing\, emotional and sometimes 
 difficult. This interactive workshop helps parents better understand thei
 r teen’s natural personality\, stress responses\, and communication style
 . You’ll learn how to reduce power struggles\, communicate more effective
 ly and support your teen’s growing independence -without losing connectio
 n. You will learn how to be practical\, compassionate and grounded in rea
 l-life parenting challenges. Walk away with fresh insight and renewed con
 fidence in your parenting.
