 ands and restaurants\, from Café Diplomatico to Mr. Christie's Cookies. B
 ut how did Toronto earn its reputation as a foodie haven?\n\nJoin culinar
 y historian Dr. Laura Carlson on a mouth-watering journey through Toronto
 ’s food history. Bring your appetite and your stretchy pants for a virtua
 l taste of past and present Toronto.\n\nPlease register online at www.tpl
 .ca http://www.tpl.ca\n\nWednesday\, May 20 from 2 pm – 3 pm\n\nMalvern B
 ranch\, Toronto Public Library\n\n30 Sewells Road\n\n(416) 396-8969
