SUMMARY: TORONTO TRANSIT COMMISSION (TTC) BOARD
DESCRIPTION:Attend the Meeting: TTC Board meetings are conducted in a hyb
 rid format\, allowing for both in-person attendance at Toronto City Hall 
 and virtual participation. Meetings are live-streamed and archived on the
  TTC's YouTube Channel.\n\nMake a Deputation (Speak at the Meeting): To a
 ddress the Board\, register in advance by emailing commissionservices@ttc
 .ca mailto:commissionservices@ttc.ca . Include your name\, any organizati
 on you represent\, the agenda item number and title\, and a brief descrip
 tion of your remarks. Registration deadline: 12:00 p.m. (noon) the busine
